{"title":"Wolf Tooth Remote Pro Dropper Lever Now Comes in Colors","link":"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-remote-pro-dropper-lever-now-comes-in-colors/","date":1706142317000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1664\" height=\"1111\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote pro shown in various anodized colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors.jpg 1664w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-768x513.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Got a <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=18985&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fremote-pro-colors%2Fproducts%2Fremote-pro-colors\">Wolf Tooth Components Remote Pro</a> dropper lever but wish it were more colorful? Or been holding out because black ain’t your thing? Well, now they’ve got you covered.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Remote Pro can now be had in one of nine colors – purple, silver (raw), espresso, blue, gold, olive, orange, red, and… black. It comes attached to a clamp for standard handlebars (22.2mm I.D.), with a universal design that works with most any brand dropper seatpost.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1046\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2.jpg\" alt=\"wolf tooth components remote pro shown in various anodized colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2-297x259.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2-800x697.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2-120x105.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/wolftooth-components-remote-pro-colors-2-768x669.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It spins on a cam, pulling more cable at first to get things going quickly, and the whole thing is highly adjustable with lots of different direct-mount compatibility with lots of different brake brands.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Already got the Remote Pro? Just add the lever blade for $19.95, it bolts on in under a minute.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=18985&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Fremote-pro-colors%2Fproducts%2Fremote-pro-colors\">WolfToothComponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wolf-tooth-remote-pro-dropper-lever-now-comes-in-colors/\">Wolf Tooth Remote Pro Dropper Lever Now Comes in Colors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"42f3245239ecd536fe047bcdae861f593ae0df9afc9e5b15836843960a0f993c","category":"Cycling"}